#+TITLE: Credits and Legal Infomation

* Work of others
Some part of my configuration is build on work of other people. In order to aknowledge their contribution, I list them here alphabetically:

** ambrevar: Pierre Neidhardt
His [[https://ambrevar.xyz/index.html][blog]] ([[https://gitlab.com/ambrevar/ambrevar.gitlab.io/-/blob/master/COPYING][GPLv3]]) and [[https://gitlab.com/ambrevar/dotfiles][dotfiles]] ([[https://gitlab.com/ambrevar/dotfiles/-/blob/master/COPYING][GPLv3]]) inspired me to find my own configuration.
** DistroTube: Derek Taylor
Another [[https://www.youtube.com/DistroTube][Youtuber]] ([[https://odysee.com/@DistroTube:2][Odysee Video Channel]]) with his own [[https://distro.tube/][blog]], sharing his [[https://gitlab.com/dwt1/dotfiles][dotfiles via GitLab]].
